casebody.data:
No. 5,

Original,

October Term, 1950.

New Jersey v. New York et al. H. Albert Young, Attorney General, and Vincent A. Theisen, Chief Deputy Attorney General, for the State of Delaware.

The motion of the State of Delaware for leave to intervene and to file an answer to the amended petition of the City of New York for modification of the decree is granted and the answer is referred to the Special Master.
